column5: Time to fish. Ice still to the shore on most lakes, but it is turning black. We hear that ice is gone in Kenora and almost in Dryden. For daily updates check my blog at www.viking-island.blogspot.com
Enid, thanks for keeping us up to date on ice conditions.
just got back from my cabin in Mcneely bay ice is about 10 feet from shore. Temp. is 39deg. tonite 24deg. but atfer tonite no more below freezing nites. Then the ice should go pretty fast!!!
